Let me clear something up. I've been a Mage since before you played with your first warder or even were just a glimmer in some developer's eye. I was a raiding Mage from before pets got neutral faction, I was a grouping Mage when no one wanted us. I was a Rod whore and I was a CoH slave. I have seen my very own suggestions stolen and implemented in the Beastlord class, only to have it bit us in the ass by having pets that come too close to ours. I have seen the glory days of usefull pets and the slow agonizing decline of my class. I have held onto some glimmer of hope that one day the devs will listen and fix my class. After 5 years of nerfs and (even worse) having our own ideas (Beastlords) and data (pet canni and the slow stick nerf) used by Sony to injure us has made that small glimmer almost die. In place of it is a smoldering brand that , should the situation arise, can be stoked into an inferno. 
<br />

<br />
I refuse to let my class die, either directly from Sony or indirectly from us being marginalized and made less unique. I will not roll over to Beastlords like yourself who feel that you should have a pet that equals ours. I refuse to let this die untill the day in which the servers are taken down, or I have my own personal Rangnorok and my EverQuest account is enveloped by the all devouring beast of retirement.
