			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I don't care about beastlord pets, and probably most other players besides the beastlords themselves care about them either.  Just like nobody really cares about mage pets until they start to out-dps player characters.  People just don't like to see a brainless naked pet do their job (melee) better then they can.
<br />

<br />
All most people care about is utility and total DPS.  I don't care if beastlordX has a pet that is so close to mine that nobody can tell the difference.  All that matters is total damage, and mages are the clear winner there.  Looking at beast utility, mini shm buffs, mini brells, slow, paragon, SD, snare via pets, beastlords have an advantage even greater than the DPS disparity.
<br />

<br />
If a mage can do say 450 DPS to every mob in a slow pulling group and a beastlord can do 250 + slow + buffs + paragon... the group can take the beastlord and give the shaman's spot to another DPS.  Everyone can do some DPS, and most do it well enough that the difference between one DPS class and another is hardly noticeable in an XP gained per hour sense.  A couple AFKs here and there easily over-shadow that margin anyways.
<br />

<br />
On the other hand, players tend to value buffs and utility far more than their face value.  They love having the buffs just because they like to see the hp number in their UI or the buff icon in the box.  Not because they think an extra 300 hp is likely to save them, but because it makes them feel better to have them.  The whole motivating factor in EQ is to make your character better, and buffs do that, even if only temporarily.
<br />

<br />
I've seen clerics gate from groups and go on a 30 minute KEI voyage, and meanwhile the whole group just sits there patiently.  After all, we wouldn't want to have to stop and med every 20 pulls.. OMG, we would lose all that XP!  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_think.gif" alt="Think" border="0" /> Nevermind the 30 minutes we just sat waiting for the cleric to go get his mind buffs...   <img src="images/smiles/eusa_wall.gif" alt="Brick wall" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=546815" target=_blank>Sarye Starfyre</a> 
<br />
Blood Cult
<br />
Xev</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
